sentences: At twelve he performed a Stevie Ray Vaughan classic from Texas Flood in a Norwegian talent competition; in 2007 he was awarded the City of Bergen's talent prize; at 16 he won the Notodden Blues Festival contest for blues guitarists.
“Guitar Superstar 2011” competition hosted by guitarist Larry Carlton.
He played guitar on Justin Bieber's "Roller Coaster" in 2013 and on Michael Jackson’s posthumous album Xscape in 2014.
